---
title: Cheesy Grilled Chicken and Bacon Burgers with Golden Wedges and BBQ-Ranch Sauce
description: Not a smash burger, but just as smashable! Kicked up with smoky bacon and sweet grilled onions, it's delectable down to the last bite.
